00:24:31.630 --> 00:24:33.280 align:middle line:84%
be very, very
difficult for a person

00:24:33.280 --> 00:24:35.295 align:middle line:90%
to do by themselves at home.

00:24:35.295 --> 00:24:38.350 align:middle line:84%
>> Buddha asked Ananda,
what's the most important part

00:24:38.350 --> 00:24:39.370 align:middle line:90%
of teaching?

00:24:39.370 --> 00:24:40.185 align:middle line:90%
Is it the teaching?

00:24:40.185 --> 00:24:42.430 align:middle line:84%
Or is it the Dharma
or the Sangha?

00:24:42.430 --> 00:24:46.000 align:middle line:84%
And so Ananda said, it's the
teaching, it's you, the Buddha.

00:24:46.000 --> 00:24:47.050 align:middle line:90%
And he said, no.

00:24:47.050 --> 00:24:48.940 align:middle line:84%
The most important
thing in spiritual life

00:24:48.940 --> 00:24:51.430 align:middle line:90%
is the sangha, or the satsung.

00:24:51.430 --> 00:24:54.700 align:middle line:84%
People who are working
together, individually

00:24:54.700 --> 00:24:56.830 align:middle line:90%
together, on the path.

00:24:56.830 --> 00:25:00.730 align:middle line:84%
We help each other stay
centered, focused, and heading

00:25:00.730 --> 00:25:02.350 align:middle line:90%
in the right direction.

00:25:02.350 --> 00:25:05.320 align:middle line:84%
