a particular mantra.

00:26:00.290 --> 00:26:01.890 align:middle line:90%
So that could be anything.

00:26:01.890 --> 00:26:03.470 align:middle line:90%
It could be om.

00:26:03.470 --> 00:26:08.150 align:middle line:84%
It could be om shri
matre namaha if you're

00:26:08.150 --> 00:26:10.096 align:middle line:90%
a follower of the goddess.

00:26:10.096 --> 00:26:12.320 align:middle line:84%
>> A mala helps you
to be more focused.

00:26:12.320 --> 00:26:13.850 align:middle line:90%
It's a physical stimulus.

00:26:13.850 --> 00:26:16.190 align:middle line:84%
So you can use it during
your meditation time.

00:26:16.190 --> 00:26:18.770 align:middle line:84%
