and to keep you on the track.

00:26:27.602 --> 00:26:36.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Om sri matre namaha,
om sri matre namaha,

00:26:36.830 --> 00:26:41.200 align:middle line:90%
om sri matre nahama.

00:26:41.200 --> 00:26:45.740 align:middle line:84%
