factors of that you can do.

00:26:49.640 --> 00:26:51.440 align:middle line:90%
So that would be japa practice.

00:26:51.440 --> 00:26:54.770 align:middle line:84%
And typically it's
done silently,

00:26:54.770 --> 00:26:57.080 align:middle line:84%
sort of kind of under
the breath where you

00:26:57.080 --> 00:26:58.871 align:middle line:90%
move your lips a little bit.

00:26:58.871 --> 00:27:00.620 align:middle line:84%
And then there are
times when you can just

00:27:00.620 --> 00:27:02.376 align:middle line:84%
